Subject: Re: [PATCH] -mm (2.4.26-rc3-mm1) v2  Smack using capabilities 32 and 33
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
